title: Setting Boundaries in Relationships
description:
Whether it's with a life partner or a friend, you've got to set boundaries with people so they don't take advantage of you. This week, Tasia and Camo discuss how they set strict limits with people to avoid drama and what the warning signs are of a fake person who probably can't be trusted.
Watch "Unfazed and Unbothered" on YouTube
